snippet: Bria Holmes had a career-high 31 points and Taylor Palmer surpassed the 1,000 point-mark on Saturday as No. 17 West Virginia defeated Kansas 84-44....

headline.print_headline: Holmes Leads No. 17 WVU Women Past K-State 84-44
headline.main: Holmes Leads No. 17 WVU Women Past K-State 84-44

lead_paragraph: Bria Holmes had a career-high 31 points and Taylor Palmer surpassed the 1,000 point-mark on Saturday as No. 17 West Virginia defeated Kansas 84-44.
